oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Photograph of Archibald (Archable) M. Duggan and Anna Caroline Shultz
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Copy photograph of Civil War veteran Archibald McMahan Duggan and his wife, Anna Caroline Shultz. Duggan was a private of Co. E, 2nd Tenn. Cav. Regt., USA. The couple lived in Sevier County and are buried in a family cemetery on Piney Road in Sevierville, Tenn.
